public class WASFGA<S extends Solution<?>>
extends AbstractMOMBI<S>
implements InteractiveAlgorithm<S,​java.util.List<S>>
Implementation of the preference based algorithm named WASF-GA on jMetal5.0
Author:
Juanjo Durillo This algorithm is described in the paper: A.B. Ruiz, R. Saborido, M. Luque "A Preference-based Evolutionary Algorithm for Multiobjective Optimization: The Weighting Achievement Scalarizing Function Genetic Algorithm". Journal of Global Optimization. May 2015, Volume 62, Issue 1, pp 101-129 DOI = {10.1007/s10898-014-0214-y}
